---
// Hero Section - Sección principal de la landing page
---

<section id="inicio" class="relative min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Imagen de fondo optimizada -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
    <picture>
      <source
        srcset="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1574629810360-7efbbe195018?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1800&q=80"
        media="(min-width: 1024px)"
      />
      <source
        srcset="/fotos/15.jpeg"
        media="(min-width: 640px)"
      />
      <img
        src="/fotos/15.jpeg"
        alt="Niños jugando fútbol celebrando en el campo"
      class="w-full h-full object-cover"
      loading="eager" 
      decoding="async"
        fetchpriority="high"
    />
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-pfc-black/80 via-pfc-black/70 to-pfc-black/90"></div>
  </div>

  <!-- Contenido del Hero -->
  <div class="relative z-10 container mx-auto px-4 text-center text-white py-20">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto fade-in" style="animation-delay: 0.2s;">
      <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-bold mb-6 leading-tight">
        Promesas Fútbol Club
        <span class="text-pfc-red block mt-2">Manizales</span>
      </h1>

      <p class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold mb-4 text-pfc-gray-light">
        Donde la pasión por el fútbol se convierte en talento
      </p>

      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl mb-6 text-pfc-gray-light italic">
        "Formando campeones para la cancha y para la vida"
      </p>

      <p class="text-base md:text-lg mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-gray-300">
        Entrenamientos personalizados para niñas y niños de 4 a 12 años con metodología integral,
        acompañamiento familiar y enfoque en valores.
      </p>

      <!-- CTA principal -->
      <a
        href="https://wa.me/573025150090?text=Hola,%20me%20gustar%C3%ADa%20agendar%20una%20clase%20de%20prueba."
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 bg-pfc-red text-white px-8 md:px-12 py-4 md:py-5 rounded-full text-lg md:text-xl font-bold hover:bg-red-600 transition-all hover:scale-105 shadow-2xl"
      >
        <svg class="w-7 h-7" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
          <path d="M17.472 14.382c-.297-.149-1.758-.867-2.03-.967-.273-.099-.471-.148-.67.15-.197.297-.767.966-.94 1.164-.173.199-.347.223-.644.075-.297-.15-1.255-.463-2.39-1.475-.883-.788-1.48-1.761-1.653-2.059-.173-.297-.018-.458.13-.606.134-.133.298-.347.446-.52.149-.174.198-.298.298-.497.099-.198.05-.371-.025-.52-.075-.149-.669-1.612-.916-2.207-.242-.579-.487-.5-.669-.51-.173-.008-.371-.01-.57-.01-.198 0-.52.074-.792.372-.272.297-1.04 1.016-1.04 2.479 0 1.462 1.065 2.875 1.213 3.074.149.198 2.096 3.2 5.077 4.487.709.306 1.262.489 1.694.625.712.227 1.36.195 1.871.118.571-.085 1.758-.719 2.006-1.413.248-.694.248-1.289.173-1.413-.074-.124-.272-.198-.57-.347m-5.421 7.403h-.004a9.87 9.87 0 01-5.031-1.378l-.361-.214-3.741.982.998-3.648-.235-.374a9.86 9.86 0 01-1.51-5.26c.001-5.45 4.436-9.884 9.888-9.884 2.64 0 5.122 1.03 6.988 2.898a9.825 9.825 0 012.893 6.994c-.003 5.45-4.437 9.884-9.885 9.884m8.413-18.297A11.815 11.815 0 0012.05 0C5.495 0 .16 5.335.157 11.892c0 2.096.547 4.142 1.588 5.945L.057 24l6.305-1.654a11.882 11.882 0 005.683 1.448h.005c6.554 0 11.89-5.335 11.893-11.893a11.821 11.821 0 00-3.48-8.413Z" />
        </svg>
        Quiero una clase de prueba
      </a>

      <div class="mt-5 flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4 text-sm md:text-base">
        <a
          href="#contacto"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 rounded-full border border-white/40 text-white/90 hover:text-white hover:border-white transition-colors"
        >
          <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 7V3m8 4V3m-9 8h10M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-3.172a2 2 0 01-1.414-.586l-.828-.828A2 2 0 0011.172 3H8a2 2 0 00-2 2v14a2 2 0 002 2z" />
          </svg>
          Ver horarios y tarifas
        </a>
        <a
          href="#faq"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 rounded-full bg-white/10 text-white/90 hover:bg-white/20 transition-colors"
        >
          <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 10h.01M12 14h.01M16 10h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0zm-9 5h.01" />
          </svg>
          Preguntas frecuentes
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-12 flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-8 text-sm md:text-base">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-pfc-red" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 01180z" />
          </svg>
          <span>Clase de prueba gratuita</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-pfc-red" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 4.354a4 4 0 110 5.292M15 21H3v-1a6 6 0 0112 0v1zm0 0h6v-1a6 6 0 00-9-5.197M13 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0z" />
          </svg>
          <span>Entrenadores certificados</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-pfc-red" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z" />
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" />
          </svg>
          <span>Campus deportivo en Manizales, Caldas</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-pfc-red" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8c1.657 0 3-1.343 3-3S13.657 2 12 2 9 3.343 9 5s1.343 3 3 3zM6 22v-2a4 4 0 014-4h4a4 4 0 014 4v2" />
          </svg>
          <span>Grupos por edades con cupos limitados</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="absolute bottom-8 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 animate-bounce" aria-hidden="true">
    <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 14l-7 7m0 0l-7-7m7 7V3" />
    </svg>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  @keyframes bounce {
    0%, 100% {
      transform: translateY(0) translateX(-50%);
    }
    50% {
      transform: translateY(-10px) translateX(-50%);
    }
  }

  .animate-bounce {
    animation: bounce 2s infinite;
  }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .animate-bounce {
      animation: none;
    }
  }
</style>
